      For most players, the choice comes down to playstyle and monster matchup. Heaven-Sent excels
      in fights where you can maintain good positioning and avoid direct hits, while Master's Touch
      provides more consistent performance across all situations. I tend to favor Heaven-Sent for
      monsters because it's more comfortable to play and I have the one shot protection for the
      cases where I do get hit.
    </p>
  </Section>

