      Choosing between Heaven-Sent and Master's Touch comes down to your comfort level and the
      specific hunt. Master's Touch builds maintain consistent performance even when taking hits,
      while Heaven-Sent offers higher peaks but requires better play to maintain its buffs. buffs.
    </p>

