      One important note: Elemental builds heavily rely on Leaping Thrust as your main damage
      dealer. When fighting monsters with good elemental hitzones (25+ preferred), these builds can
      significantly outperform raw builds. Guard Dash into Leaping Thrust should be your go-to combo
